Takish'hiz should sound familiar, as its been in EQ lore since the beginning. It's actually two cities, the elven holy city in the Plane of Growth, and the Norrathian version (named after the original) that was built around where the Desert of Ro is now. Maybe it was ripped off from Takhsis, but... enh.<br>
